B6AUD.original: ~z~Why do you think I put my neck on the line for you?
B6AUD.translated: ~z~你以为我为什么肯为你把头别在裤腰带上？

B6AUD.original: ~z~If you're getting smart about seeing Angie at my place then you can button it.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~你要是想暗示在我的地方见到Angie就闭嘴。

B6AUD.original: ~z~Frankie's one guy, he can disappear real easy if the Feds show. Plus, he's a smart kid.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~Frankie是平民，就算FIB出现也能脱身。而且，他聪明得很。

B6AUD.original: ~z~The Feds know that wiseguys run their mouths, they love it.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~FIB知道黑手党满嘴跑火车，他们就喜欢这个。

B6AUD.original: ~z~Put your bags down and lie on the ground.
~z~Shut up, these Feds are all over me.
~z~Niko, they're all over us. We're ditching the cars and going on foot. Park up behind me when I stop.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~Niko，他们到处都是。我们要弃车步行了。待会儿我停哪儿你停哪儿。

B6AUD.original: ~z~If you wanna get rid of the chopper there's some fire power in the back.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~你要是想除掉直升机，后面有些装备。

B6AUD.original: ~z~God, I love that kid. You wanna see a picture?
B6AUD.translated: ~z~天哪，我爱那姑娘。照片你想看吗？

B6AUD.original: ~z~-Yeah, okay. I'll see you later. ~n~-You take care now.
~z~Then maybe you wouldn't have such problems with people turning state's.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~说不定你们就不用担心有人告密了。

B6AUD.original: ~z~Nice driving, Niko. We're gonna be able to shift this H for a lot of money.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~好车技，Niko。我们可以用这些白粉换来很多钱。

B6AUD.original: ~z~Ray runs his mouth so much that no one pays much attention to what comes out of it.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~Ray满嘴跑火车，没人在意他说什么的。

B6AUD.original: ~z~I'm sorry man. It's just... I only got married the other day.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~很抱歉，伙计。只是...前几天我刚结的婚。

B6AUD.original: ~z~Dammit, Niko. We can't do this with just two of us. I'm calling it off. Ciao.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~该死，Niko。光我们两个人不行，只能先取消了。再见。

B6AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, well, that's something that Ray likes to run his mouth about.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~好吧，Ray最喜欢把这种事挂在嘴上。

B6AUD.original: ~z~There's been some fucked up shit going on but you been keeping cool.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~尽管中途出了些岔子，但你还是十分冷静。

B6AUD.original: ~z~We're heading back up to that old house off Beaverhead Avenue in Westdyke.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~我们要回到Westdyke区Beaverhead大道的老房子那边。

B6AUD.original: ~z~Well, you can't count on nothing going right. That's the lesson I've learnt today.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~好吧，你不能指望事事顺利。这就是我今天学到的教训。

B6AUD.original: ~z~A Fed don't care if he's taking someone down on a legitimate beef or if it's total bullshit.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~FIB不在乎抓人靠的是证据确凿还是一堆屁话。

B6AUD.original: ~z~Might just keep the Pegorino family's head above water. See you around.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~也许能给Pegorino家族的财政续上一会儿。回头见。

B6AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, you fucking laugh. Laugh all you want.
~z~Don't think about it. He fucked up today and he paid the price.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~别再想了。这次他搞砸了，就付出了代价。

B6AUD.original: ~z~Shit, you might be right there but that's only an attitude that'd work for a lone gun like you.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，你可能是对的，但这种态度只适合你这种孤军奋战的人。

B6AUD.original: ~z~If only the Feds knew how full of shit most wiseguys were.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~要是FIB知道多数黑手党有多会扯淡，

B6AUD.original: ~z~You're a good earner. I got respect for you.
~z~You can if you do everything yourself. If you don't rely on anybody else.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~如果你自己做每件事你就能做到。如果你不依赖别人。

B6AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, call it a cooling off period. We took it, but we don't know who was watching it beforehand.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~是啊，算是种冷静期吧。货到手了，但不知道有没有被人盯上。

B6AUD.original: ~z~I believe it. I'd be dead already if Jimmy P listened to anything he'd said about me.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~是这样。要是Jimmy P信了他说的我的事，我早死了。

B6AUD.original: ~z~This thing of ours is built upon trust for everyone else in the family.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~我们这件事是建立在对家里其他人的信任之上的。

B6AUD.original: ~z~Niko, that's the van. We gotta get back to the pizza place in Westdyke.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~Niko，就是那辆货车。我们得回Westdyke的披萨店。

B6AUD.original: ~z~We can't let those Feds run the boss off the road, get them.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~不能让那些条子把老板的车掀翻，干掉他们。

B6AUD.original: ~z~Fuck. He was a good kid, but he screwed up today and now he paid for it.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~操。他是个好孩子，但他今天搞砸了，现在他为此付出了代价。

B6AUD.original: ~z~Hey, let's see if we get back before you start talking like this, shall we?
B6AUD.translated: ~z~喂，这些有的没的等我们平安抵达了再说，好吗？

B6AUD.original: ~z~The two of us is just friends. We talk.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~我们只是普通朋友。聊天而已。

B6AUD.original: ~z~As long as he can get his face in the newspaper and a blowjob from his wife, he's happy.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~只要能在报纸上露脸，老婆肯口一次，他就高兴了。

B6AUD.original: ~z~You and me are only here today because we didn't make the fuckup that Frankie did.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~你我现在还活着，是因为我们没像Frankie那样把事搞砸。

B6AUD.original: ~z~Shit. Uncle Phil's gone forever. Don't tell the other guys you saw me crying, okay?
B6AUD.translated: ~z~妈的。Phil叔叔永远走了。别告诉其他人你看到我哭了，好吗？

B6AUD.original: ~z~So, it's been long enough. You think we're gonna be okay to pick it up? No trouble?
B6AUD.translated: ~z~已经放了很久了，现在就能不受妨碍顺利转移了？你这么想的？

B6AUD.original: ~z~Shit, I don't know how much more of this I can take.
~z~The Feds don't fuck with the boss and get away with it. Get close to them.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~条子给我老板添乱还想跑？快追上去。

B6AUD.original: ~z~These cops ain't flipping me if I'm caught. And they better not flip you either.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~我被抓了绝不会向他们告发。你最好也不会告发。

B6AUD.original: ~z~I need to find something out about someone. Maybe you can help.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~我需要调查某人的情报。也许你能帮忙。

B6AUD.original: ~z~That's what keeps me alive and outta the pen. We'll see when we get there.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~所以我还能活在监狱外面。到那里就知道了。

B6AUD.original: ~z~Get me close to the boss and I'll take out that Fed car.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~往老板那边靠，我来解决警车。

B6AUD.original: ~z~Shit, I ain't made for this sort of stress. Can we lose the heat already?
B6AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，我要顶不住了。能不能快点甩掉条子？

B6AUD.original: ~z~Frankie, Niko, grab the stuff from the trunk and follow me. I got a van we can use.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~Frankie，Niko，拿上后备箱的货跟我走。我有辆小货车可以用。

B6AUD.original: ~z~The Feds are all over us, man.
~z~Don't lose the boss, man. I got no idea where we're headin'.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~别跟丢老板，伙计。我不知道目的地是哪儿。

B6AUD.original: ~z~We both gotta take a lot of shit from Jimmy and it helps to speak about it.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~我们都被Jimmy弄得很憋屈，互相聊聊挺好的。

B6AUD.original: ~z~He fucked up. Us unloading the H was his call.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~他搞砸了。叫我们来转移白粉也是他的决定。
~z~糟了，我们要跟丢他了。我们要完了。

B6AUD.original: ~z~Look, I don't ever assume something's gonna go down easy, without any trouble.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~听着，我从不认为有什么事能顺顺利利、不受妨碍。

B6AUD.original: ~z~You know, since you don't look like you're full of crap,
B6AUD.translated: ~z~你知道吗，你也不像是满嘴假话的人，

B6AUD.original: ~z~Damn, this is a wild ride. I didn't think I was gonna come outta that one.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，这次太惊险了。我还以为自己要没命了。

B6AUD.original: ~z~The Feds aren't learning their lesson, there's more of them.
~z~You don't notice the fifty feds watching these cars?
~z~We don't got all day, come on.
~z~Let's hustle Niko... move it, move it, move it.
~z~You're fucking lucky that you did. Lucky any of us did.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~没死真的算你走运，活着的都走运。

B6AUD.original: ~z~I ain't seen a soul, boss. It's a ghost house.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~人影都没见着一个，老板。就一鬼屋。

B6AUD.original: ~z~So, you just left it with Frankie?
~z~Ray's gonna be pleased about this. He's been trying to bang Frankie's wife ever since they got married.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~Ray会很高兴的。自从Frankie结婚，Ray就想睡他老婆。

B6AUD.original: ~z~We will fire if you fail to surrender what you are carrying.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~再不交出身上的东西就范，我们就要开枪了。

B6AUD.original: ~z~You got a wife, you got a ma, don't play around with your life.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~你娶了媳妇，上又有老母，别拿自己的命开玩笑。

B6AUD.original: ~z~As long as we don't see any helicopters, vans, suspicious gardeners talking into earpieces.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~只要我们没见着什么直升机啊、厢型车啊、可疑的园丁对着耳机讲电话啊，

B6AUD.original: ~z~Get a move on, we ain't sight seeing over here.
~z~So do us all a favor and keep quiet.
~z~Don't I know it, Phil. I shoulda seen 'em.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~确实如此，Phil。我应该要发现他们的。

B6AUD.original: ~z~Okay, I had word from Frankie, my nephew.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~好了，我收到我侄子Frankie的消息了。

B6AUD.original: ~z~Shit, we can't stash the stuff with the cops on our backs, lose 'em.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，我们不能背着警察把东西藏起来，扔了。

B6AUD.original: ~z~Frankie, you been keeping your eyes open out here?
~z~Don't play around with other people's lives either.
~z~Poor girl. She ain't got much hope left now.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~可怜的姑娘。她的人生一片灰暗。

B6AUD.original: ~z~Drop your guns and your bags, now. Let us take you into custody.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~放下你们的枪和包。老老实实接受逮捕。

B6AUD.original: ~z~Put your foot down, catch up to him.
~z~Niko, get in that car and follow me.
~z~I've been telling Niko I got a lot on my mind.
~z~No one's been paying undue attention to the H we took off the Triads.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~没人盯着我们从三合会那儿弄来的白粉。

B6AUD.original: ~z~Gimme a break, man. I got a lot on my mind, you know?
B6AUD.translated: ~z~饶了我吧，伙计。我顾不过来，懂吗？

B6AUD.original: ~z~I don't want to take a bullet or a stint in the pen for anyone else's fuck up.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~我不想为别人的失误去蹲监狱或者挨枪子儿。

B6AUD.original: ~z~I got the horse loaded into two cars for you.
~z~Ah God, we're gonna lose the boss.
~z~This is one more reason for my ex-wife to hate my guts. He was her nephew, man.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~我前妻又多了个恨我的理由。这是她侄子啊，兄弟。

B6AUD.original: ~z~Next time, mind on the job. This ain't a fucking joke.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~下一次，多顾着点工作。别拿这事儿当儿戏。

B6AUD.original: ~z~Shit, Niko. My half ain't in too good shape neither but I don't wanna tell the skip we lost it all. Ciao.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，Niko。我这份看起来也不太好，但我不想告诉老大我们全弄丢了。再见。

B6AUD.original: ~z~Sniper on the roof, keep your heads down.
~z~I don't feel comfortable with all these cops on us.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~警察一直在追，让我很不舒服。

B6AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, we put it in an isolated place, hopefully any attention it was getting would be noticed.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~对，我们故意找了个偏僻的地方，很容易知道货有没有被人盯上。

B6AUD.original: ~z~Maybe I can give you a call?
~z~If none of that's going on then we're okay?
B6AUD.translated: ~z~没见着这些的话就安全了是吧？

B6AUD.original: ~z~I thought it was a wedding present for your nephew?
B6AUD.translated: ~z~不是送你侄子当新婚礼物了吗？

B6AUD.original: ~z~Maybe then you can spend time with your wife instead of some jailhouse bitch.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~否则你就到监狱里找婊子吧，有老婆也没用。

B6AUD.original: ~z~It's about time to pick up that H that my nephew's been sitting on.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~现在该去转移我侄子把守的白粉了。

B6AUD.original: ~z~There's no way out of this. Give up your bags and weapons.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~你们无路可逃。交出你们的包和武器。

B6AUD.original: ~z~Phil, that stuff ain't around anymore. We lost it.
~z~Can you get these cops off of us?
~z~And my sister, I been putting her through college.
~z~I don't mean to take advantage, but...
~z~he can ask the bitch to take it out of the divorce settlement. Fucking cunt.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~不想要就让那个贱人从离婚协议里去掉啊。混蛋婊子。

B6AUD.original: ~z~He's my nephew through my ex-wife, I might give him work sometimes but I ain't gonna give him this load of horse.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~他是我前妻那边的侄子，我偶尔会找他干活，但绝不可能把这批海马送他。

B6AUD.original: ~z~I don't want to see a fucking picture. I'm trying to get us out of this situation.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~我他妈的不看。老子忙着摆脱条子追捕。

B6AUD.original: ~z~I didn't have much time to scope this out. My ma's kinda sick. I been looking after her.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~我没空盯着这边。我妈身体不好，一直是我照顾。

B6AUD.original: ~z~He wants anything except a bit of muscle work
~z~You had any more girlfriends since the ex-wife?
B6AUD.translated: ~z~离婚以后你还找过女朋友吗？

B6AUD.original: ~z~This ain't over until we got the H in a safe place.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~没把白粉送到安全的地方就还没结束。

B6AUD.original: ~z~God they ain't making it easy, are they?
B6AUD.translated: ~z~天哪，他们就是不肯放水是吧？

B6AUD.original: ~z~Can't these fucking Feds let up for a minute.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~这些屌毛条子就不能消停一会儿吗。

B6AUD.original: ~z~Niko, that's the van. We gotta get to a safe house.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~Niko，就是那辆货车。我们得去安全屋。

B6AUD.original: ~z~Shit Frankie, you dumb fuck. The Feds have been watching us all along.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，Frankie，你个傻逼。FIB一直在盯着我们。

B6AUD.original: ~z~He's related to my ex-wife and she was smart enough to ruin my life with one law suit.
B6AUD.translated: ~z~他是我前妻的亲戚。我前妻则聪明到仅靠一纸诉讼就毁了我的人生。
